quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,91,"Balia bakhola Ikurani okhuba ebitonyetonye."
  15,92,"Kho nditsuba khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi mbu, toto khulibareeba boosi."
  15,93,"Khukalia koosi akabakholanga."
  15,94,"Kho yusia akawalomesibwa, ne obe ehale nende abatsokaasi."
  15,95,"Toto efwe khukhuyela okhukhulinda okhurulana nende abakhubayilanga."
  15,96,"Balia abatsokaasinjia Nyasaye nende abanyasaye bandi, kho balitsa okhumanya."
  15,97,"Ne toto khwamanya mbu eshilifu shishio shinyoolanga obusiro khukalia akababoolanga."
  15,98,"Kho tswenula Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khukhumwitsoomia, ne obe halala nende bamwinamilanga nibasujuda."
  15,99,"Ne olaame Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi okhuula likhuulile eliatoto elo (lifwa)."
  16,1,"Likhuwa lia Nyasaye liloola butswa, kho mulaliyungubasia tawe. Obutswenufu nobubwe, ne ali hekulu muno wa akabamutsokaasinjia ninako."
  16,2,"Yeshinjia abalaika nende obufimbuli, khubuchami bubwe khu ulia owayenya mubasumba bebe, mbu: “Kanyilisie (Abandu) mbu abulaho nyasaye wundi owulali Esie tawe, kho murie esie.”"
  16,3,"Yaloonga likulu nende eshialo khubwatoto, ali hekulu muno wa ebiabamutsokasinjia ninabio."
  16,4,"Yaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende indonyande yamatsi kolwibulo, mana naye naba omuyingasi owa habulafu."
  16,5,"Ne yaloonga tsisolo, mwetso munyoolangamwo obutundumu nende obukhoonyi, ne etsindi mutsilitsanga."
  16,6,"Ne mulolanga obulayi olwa mutsikalusinjia ingolobe nende shingala mutsiyilanga mushiayo itsuli."